graph TD
    accTitle: Quality Control Workflow
    accDescr: Parallel execution of FastQC, Mosdepth, and Picard, consolidated finally through MultiQC.

    raw_fastqs[📦 **Raw** FASTQs] --> fastqc[⚙️ **FastQC**]

    alignment_bam[📦 **alignment** BAM] --> mosdepth[⚙️ **Mosdepth**]
    alignment_bam --> picard_tools[⚙️ **Picard** Tools]
    alignment_bam --> samtools_stats[⚙️ **samtools** stats]

    fastp_report[📝 **fastp** report JSON] --> multiqc[⚙️ **MultiQC**]

    fastqc --> multiqc
    mosdepth --> multiqc
    picard_tools --> multiqc
    samtools_stats --> multiqc

    multiqc --> multiqc_report[📝 **multiqc_DNA** HTML]

    classDef primary fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#2563eb,stroke-width:2px,color:#1e3a5f
    classDef success fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,stroke-width:2px,color:#14532d

    class raw_fastqs,alignment_bam,fastp_report primary
    class multiqc_report success
